#hm-note[
  *Note on the Golden Chain:* Alchemical symbols found in the original GCH text are presented to students through allegory and plain-language equivalents, in keeping with the tradition of veiling the Art. Students at each tier receive access only to the corresponding Book (Tyro → Book I; Initiate → Book II; Adept → Book III). The headmaster should not issue subsequent Books early under any circumstances.

  *Note on QMed and QTar:* The QUAREIA inner work lessons are the intellectual property of Josephine McCarthy and are published under specific licensing terms. Content drawn from these lessons is presented throughout the curriculum in substantially reworded form. Students never receive original lesson documents. When in doubt about whether a passage is sufficiently reworded, err toward paraphrase.
]
